PROFILE LOCATION
----------------
In a small slope. Snow depth is variable at profile location. Ground cover is grass.

PROFILE
-------
Very low hardness, shallow snowpack.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
After several jumps part of the block broke at the skis. CT and ECT provided similar results, failure in same depths.

SNOW SURFACE
------------
New snow, penetration depth 20 cm. Soft/loose snow. Crust on windexposed bumps.

SNOW DRIFT
----------
Variable new snow depth.

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
No

AVALANCHES
----------
Small sluffing in extremely steep terrain.

AVALANCHE DANGER
----------------
2. We only covered limited terrain, where we traveled moderate.</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2019-02-12T13:15:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2019-02-12T16:45:29+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2019-02-12T17:45:36+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos - Pischa</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>2280</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>SW</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>35</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.900464 46.814777</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">138.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-7.5</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">138.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">2.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>PP</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>PPgp</caaml:grainFormSecondary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>2.0</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>3.0</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">2.0